name: Cancer Llama
description: Cancer Llama is a very sentimental Llama. He is ruled by the moon and guided by his emotions. Though this could be a challenge when facing tough decisions, Cancer Llama truly loves and cares for all his other star sign llama friends. When they need help dealing with the stress and responsibility of being a Zodiac Llama, Cancer is there to empathize and help them find peace.
